  <para style="mt1">UMikha</para>
  <para style="imt">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="imt1">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="im">Umphrofethi uMikha ukhuluma lemibuso eseningizimu kwakoJuda ngesikhathi sombuso kaJothamu, u-Ahazi kanye loHezekhiya (emaphethelweni esentshuri yesificaminwembili uKhristu engakazalwa). Uphrofitha ukuthi iSamariya leJerusalema izigodlo zako-Israyeli zizabhidlizwa ngenxa yemithetho yazo engekho qotho, lenkolo ekhohlakeleyo. Abantu badela isivumelwano abasenza loNkulunkulu, bathatha inkolo zobuhedeni zamaKhenani. Izinothi labalamandla bahlukuluza abayanga, betshaya indiva umthetho kaMosi. UMikha uyabaxwayisa ukuthi uswazi lokungathembeki kwabo lokungahluleli ngeqiniso luyeza njalo imibuso yomibili izalwiswa inqotshwe njalo ithunjwe. Njengokubonisa kwakhe, iSamariya yanqotshwa ngama-Asiriya ngo-722 uKhristu engakazalwa, iJerusalema yona yanqotshwa ngamaKhaladiya ngo-587 kusiya emnyakeni olandelayo ka-600 uKhristu engakazalwa.</para>
  <para style="ip">Isiphrofethi sikaMikha sigudla phakathi laphakathi kwezixwayiso zokubhidlizwa lezithembiso zokuvuselelwa. Sinye ngasinye isiphrofethi sikaMikha ngobuthathu bazo, siqala ngamahlandla okwahlulelwa, besesiphetha ngezithembiso zemvuselelo. UMikha umemezela ukuthi ngozwelo langokwethembeka kwesivumelwano, uNkulunkulu uzasindisa insalela yabantu njalo ababuyisele elizweni labo. Lapho abazabuswa khona yinkosi elungileyo babe yinkazimulo yomhlaba wonke, beqondisa izizwe zonke ezindleleni <char style="nd">zikaThixo</char>. UNkulunkulu uzamsiza u-Israyeli athole indawo yakhe endabeni yebhayibhili.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="MIC 1"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MIC 1:1"/>Ilizwi <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> elafika kuMikha waseMoreshethi ensukwini zemibuso kaJothamu, loka-Ahazi loHezekhiya, amakhosi akoJuda, umbono awubonayo mayelana leSamariya leJerusalema.<verse eid="MIC 1:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MIC 1:2"/>Zwanini lonke lina bantu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:2">lalelani, awu wena mhlaba labo bonke abakuwo,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:2">ukuze <char style="nd">uThixo</char> Wobukhosi afakaze ngawe ekulahla,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:2">
    <char style="nd">uThixo</char> esethempelini lakhe elingcwele.<verse eid="MIC 1:2"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukwahlulelwa KweSamariya LeJerusalema</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MIC 1:3"/>Khangelani! <char style="nd">UThixo</char> uyeza evela lapho ahlala khona;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:3">wehlela phansi njalo enyathela ezindaweni eziphakemeyo zomhlaba.<verse eid="MIC 1:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MIC 1:4"/>Izintaba ziyancibilika ngaphansi kwakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:4">lezigodi ziyaqhekezeka phakathi</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:4">njengengcino phansi komlilo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:4">lanjengamanzi esehla ngamandla emthezukweni.<verse eid="MIC 1:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MIC 1:5"/>Konke lokhu kungenxa yokona kukaJakhobe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:5">ngenxa yezono zendlu ka-Israyeli.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:5">Kuyini ukona kukaJakhobe na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:5">AkusiSamariya na?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:5">Iyini indawo kaJuda ephakemeyo na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:5">AkusiJerusalema na?<verse eid="MIC 1:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MIC 1:6"/>“Ngakho iSamariya ngizayenza ibe yinqumbi yemfucuza,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:6">indawo yokuhlanyela izivini.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:6">Amatshe ayo ngizawathela esigodini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:6">ngiphendle lezisekelo zayo.<verse eid="MIC 1:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MIC 1:7"/>Zonke izithombe zayo zizaphohlozwa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:7">zonke izipho zayo zasethempelini zizatshiswa ngomlilo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:7">ngizaphahlaza zonke izifanekiso zayo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:7">Njengoba yaqoqa izipho zayo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:7">ngeholo lezifebe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:7">zizasetshenziswa njengeholo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:7">lezifebe futhi.”<verse eid="MIC 1:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukukhala Lokulila</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MIC 1:8"/>Ngenxa yalokhu ngizakhala ngilile;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:8">ngizahamba ngezinyawo phansi njalo nginqunu.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:8">Ngizahlaba umkhulungwane njengekhanka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:8">ngikhale njengesikhova.<verse eid="MIC 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MIC 1:9"/>Ngoba inxeba layo kalelapheki;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:9">selifikile koJuda.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:9">Selifike kulo kanye isango labantu bami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:9">kanye laseJerusalema uqobo.<verse eid="MIC 1:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MIC 1:10"/>Lingakukhulumi eGathi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:10">lingakhali lakancane.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:10">Giqikani ethulini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:10">eBhethi Ofira.<verse eid="MIC 1:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MIC 1:11"/>Dlulani linqunu njalo lilenhloni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:11">lina elihlala eShafiri.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:11">Labo abahlala eZawanani</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:11">kabayikuphuma.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:11">IBhethi-Ezeli iphakathi kokulila;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:11">ukuvikelwa kwayo kususiwe kini.<verse eid="MIC 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MIC 1:12"/>Labo abahlala eMarothi bayazijanqa ngobuhlungu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:12">belindele usizo</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:12">ngoba umonakalo uvele <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:12">wafika lasesangweni leJerusalema.<verse eid="MIC 1:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MIC 1:13"/>Lina elihlala eLakhishi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:13">bophelani amabhiza agijimayo enqoleni.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:13">Yini elaba yisisusa sesono eNdodakazini yeZiyoni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:13">ngoba ukona kuka-Israyeli kwafunyanwa kini.<verse eid="MIC 1:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MIC 1:14"/>Ngakho-ke lizanika iMoreshethi Gathi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:14">izipho zokwehlukana.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:14">Idolobho lase-Akhizibhi lizabonakalisa inkohliso</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:14">emakhosini ako-Israyeli.<verse eid="MIC 1:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MIC 1:15"/>Ngizalilethela umnqobi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:15">lina elihlala eMaresha.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:15">Lowo olodumo luka-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:15">uzakuza e-Adulami.<verse eid="MIC 1:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MIC 1:16"/>Phucani amakhanda enu likhalela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:16">abantwabenu elibathandayo;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 1:16">ziphuceni libe njengelinqe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 1:16">ngoba bazasuka kini baye ekuthunjweni.<verse eid="MIC 1:16"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MIC 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="MIC 2"/>
  <para style="s1">Amacebo Abantu LakaNkulunkulu</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MIC 2:1"/>Maye kulabo abaceba ububi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:1">kulabo abaceba ukwenza okubi emibhedeni yabo!</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 2:1">Ekudabukeni kokusa bayakwenza</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:1">ngoba kusemandleni abo ukukwenza.<verse eid="MIC 2:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MIC 2:2"/>Bahawukela amasimu bawathumbe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:2">kanye lezindlu, bazithathe.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 2:2">Badlelezela umuntu ngomuzi wakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:2">lomuntu wakibo ngelifa lakhe.<verse eid="MIC 2:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MIC 2:3"/>Ngakho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 2:3">“Ngiceba ukwenza umonakalo kulababantu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:3">elingeke liziphephise kuwo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 2:3">Kalisayikuhamba ngokuziqhenya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:3">ngoba kuzakuba yisikhathi sencithakalo.<verse eid="MIC 2:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MIC 2:4"/>Ngalolosuku abantu bazalihleka;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:4">bazaliklolodela ngale ingoma yokulila bathi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 2:4">‘Thina sichithwe okupheleleyo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:4">ilifa labantu bami labiwe.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 2:4">Uyangithathela!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:4">Amasimu ethu uwanika abathengisi.’ ”<verse eid="MIC 2:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MIC 2:5"/>Ngakho-ke kawuzukuba laye ebandleni <char style="nd">likaThixo</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:5">ozalabela ilizwe ngenkatho.<verse eid="MIC 2:5"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Abaphrofethi Bamanga</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MIC 2:6"/>Abaphrofethi babo bathi, “Lingaphrofethi.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:6">Lingaphrofethi ngalezizinto;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:6">ihlazo kaliyikusehlela.”<verse eid="MIC 2:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MIC 2:7"/>Wena ndlu kaJakhobe, kufanele yini ukuba kuthiwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:7">“UMoya <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> uzondile na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:7">Uyazenza izinto ezinje na?”</para>
  <para style="b" vid="MIC 2:7"/>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 2:7">“Amazwi ami kawenzi okulungileyo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:7">kuye ozindlela zakhe ziqondile na?<verse eid="MIC 2:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MIC 2:8"/>Okwamanje abantu bami sebehlamuke</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:8">njengesitha.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 2:8">Lihlubula ingubo eligugu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:8">kulabo abedlulayo linganakile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:8">njengabantu abavela empini.<verse eid="MIC 2:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MIC 2:9"/>Abesifazane babantu bami liyabaxotsha</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:9">emizini yabo emihle.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 2:9">Lisusa isibusiso sami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:9">kokuphela ebantwaneni babo.<verse eid="MIC 2:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MIC 2:10"/>Sukani lihambe!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:10">Ngoba le akusindawo yenu yokuphumula,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 2:10">ngoba ingcolile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:10">ichithekile, okungeke kulungiswe.<verse eid="MIC 2:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MIC 2:11"/>Nxa umqambi wamanga lomkhohlisi efika athi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:11">‘Ngizaliphrofethela iwayini elinengi lotshwala,’</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:11">uyabe engumphrofethi walababantu nje kuphela!”<verse eid="MIC 2:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isithembiso Sokukhululwa</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MIC 2:12"/>“Impela ngizalibutha lonke, wena Jakhobe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:12">impela ngizabaqoqela ndawonye abako-Israyeli abasalayo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 2:12">Ngizabaqoqela ndawonye njengezimvu esibayeni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:12">njengomhlambi wezimvu emadlelweni awo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:12">indawo ibe lokuphithizela kwabantu.<verse eid="MIC 2:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MIC 2:13"/>Lowo ozavula indlela uzahamba phambi kwabo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:13">bazafohla isango baphume.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 2:13">Inkosi yabo izadlulela phambi kwabo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 2:13">
    <char style="nd">uThixo</char> abe phambi kwabo.”<verse eid="MIC 2:13"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MIC 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="MIC 3"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukukhuzwa Kwabakhokheli Labaphrofethi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MIC 3:1"/>Lapho-ke mina ngathi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 3:1">“Lalelani lina bakhokheli bakoJakhobe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:1">lina babusi bendlu yako-Israyeli.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 3:1">Ukulunga akumelanga likwazi na,<verse eid="MIC 3:1"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MIC 3:2"/>lina elizonda okuhle lithande okubi;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 3:2">elixebula isikhumba ebantwini bami</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:2">lenyama emathanjeni abo;<verse eid="MIC 3:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MIC 3:3"/>lina elibadla inyama abantu bami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:3">lihlubule isikhumba sabo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:3">lichoboze lamathambo abo abe yizicucu;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 3:3">elibaqumaquma njengenyama yepani,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:3">lanjengenyama yembiza?”<verse eid="MIC 3:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MIC 3:4"/>Lapho-ke bazakhala <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:4">kodwa kayikubaphendula.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 3:4">Ngalesosikhathi uzabafihlela ubuso bakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:4">ngenxa yobubi ababenzileyo.<verse eid="MIC 3:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MIC 3:5"/>Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 3:5">“Okunjengabaphrofethi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:5">abedukisa abantu bami,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 3:5">umuntu angabapha ukudla,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:5">bamemezela ‘ukuthula’</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 3:5">nxa engabaphi balungisela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:5">ukumhlasela ngempi.<verse eid="MIC 3:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MIC 3:6"/>Ngakho ubusuku buzakwehlela phezu kwenu, kungekho mibono,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:6">kanye lomnyama, kungekho kuhlahlula.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 3:6">Ilanga lizabatshonela abaphrofethi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:6">losuku luzakuba mnyama kubo.<verse eid="MIC 3:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MIC 3:7"/>Ababonisayo bazayangeka</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:7">labahlahluli babe lenhloni.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 3:7">Bonke bazamboza ubuso babo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:7">ngoba kungelampendulo evela kuNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="MIC 3:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MIC 3:8"/>Kodwa mina ngiphiwe amandla,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:8">loMoya <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:8">lokulunga kanye lesibindi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 3:8">ukuba ngitshele uJakhobe ukona kwakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:8">lo-Israyeli isono sakhe.<verse eid="MIC 3:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MIC 3:9"/>Zwanini lokhu lina bakhokheli bendlu kaJakhobe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:9">lani babusi bendlu ka-Israyeli,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 3:9">eleyisa ukulunga</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:9">lihlanekele konke okuqondileyo;<verse eid="MIC 3:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MIC 3:10"/>elakha iZiyoni ngokuchitha igazi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:10">leJerusalema ngobubi.<verse eid="MIC 3:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MIC 3:11"/>Abakhokheli bayo bahlulela ngokufunjathiswa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:11">abaphristi bayo bafundisela inhlawulo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:11">labaphrofethi bayo baphrofithela imali;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 3:11">ikanti bathembele <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> njalo bathi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:11">“Kanti <char style="nd">uThixo</char> kakho phakathi kwethu na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:11">Akulancithakalo engasehlela.”<verse eid="MIC 3:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MIC 3:12"/>Ngakho-ke ngenxa yenu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:12">iZiyoni izalinywa njengensimu,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 3:12">iJerusalema izakuba yinqwaba yemfucuza,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 3:12">intaba yethempeli ibe yindunduma eyande izixukwana.<verse eid="MIC 3:12"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MIC 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="MIC 4"/>
  <para style="s1">INtaba <char style="nd">KaThixo</char></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MIC 4:1"/>Ngezinsuku zokucina</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:1">intaba yethempeli <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> izamiswa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:1">njengenhloko phakathi kwezintaba;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:1">izaphakanyiselwa phezu kwezintaba</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:1">njalo izizwe zizabekelela zisiya kuyo.<verse eid="MIC 4:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MIC 4:2"/>Izizwe ezinengi zizafika zithi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:2">“Wozani siye phezu kwentaba <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:2">siye ethempelini likaNkulunkulu kaJakhobe.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:2">Uzasifundisa izindlela zakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:2">ukuze sihambe emikhondweni yakhe.”</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:2">Umthetho uzavela eZiyoni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:2">ilizwi <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> livele eJerusalema.<verse eid="MIC 4:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MIC 4:3"/>Uzakwahlulela phakathi kwezizwe ezinengi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:3">alamule lezingxabano zezizwe ezilamandla ezindaweni ezikhatshana.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:3">Bazakhanda izinkemba zabo zibe yimihlathi yamakhuba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:3">lemikhonto yabo ibe zingqamu zokuthena izihlahla.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:3">Isizwe asiyikuhlomela isizwe ngenkemba</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:3">loba sifundele ukulwa impi futhi.<verse eid="MIC 4:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MIC 4:4"/>Umuntu wonke uzahlala ngaphansi kwesihlahla sakhe sevini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:4">langaphansi kwesihlahla sakhe somkhiwa,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:4">njalo kakho ozabenza besabe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:4">ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uSomandla usekhulumile.<verse eid="MIC 4:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MIC 4:5"/>Zonke izizwe zingahamba</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:5">ebizweni labonkulunkulu bazo;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:5">thina sizahamba ebizweni <char style="nd">likaThixo</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:5">uNkulunkulu wethu kuze kube laphakade.<verse eid="MIC 4:5"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Icebo <char style="nd">LikaThixo</char></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MIC 4:6"/>“Ngalolosuku,” kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:6">“ngizabutha abaqhulayo;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:6">ngizaqoqa abathunjwayo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:6">lalabo engabehlisela usizi.<verse eid="MIC 4:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MIC 4:7"/>Ngizakwenza abaqhulayo babe yinsalela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:7">abaxotshwayo babe yisizwe esilamandla.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:7">
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> uzababusa eNtabeni iZiyoni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:7">kusukela ngalolosuku kuze kube nininini.<verse eid="MIC 4:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MIC 4:8"/>Wena nqaba yokulinda yomhlambi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:8">wena nqaba yeNdodakazi yeZiyoni,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:8">umbuso wakuqala uzabuyiselwa kuwe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:8">ubukhosi buzakuza eNdodakazini yaseJerusalema.”<verse eid="MIC 4:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MIC 4:9"/>Kungani khathesi usukhala kakhulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:9">kawulankosi na?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:9">Umeluleki wakho usebhubhile na,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:9">ukuba uphathwe yibuhlungu obunjengowesifazane ohelelwayo?<verse eid="MIC 4:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MIC 4:10"/>Janqula ngobuhlungu, wena Ndodakazi yeZiyoni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:10">njengowesifazane ohelelwayo,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:10">ngoba khathesi sekumele usuke kulelidolobho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:10">uyehlala egangeni.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:10">Uzakuya eBhabhiloni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:10">lapho ozahlengwa khona.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:10">Khonale <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uzakukhulula</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:10">ezandleni zezitha zakho.<verse eid="MIC 4:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MIC 4:11"/>Kodwa khathesi izizwe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:11">ezinengi zikujamele.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:11">Zithi, “Kangcoliswe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:11">lamehlo ethu kawahawukele iZiyoni!”<verse eid="MIC 4:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MIC 4:12"/>Kodwa kabayazi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:12">imicabango <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:12">kabaliqedisisi icebo lakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:12">yena obabutha njengezixha zamabele esizeni.<verse eid="MIC 4:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MIC 4:13"/>“Sukuma ubhule, wena Ndodakazi yeZiyoni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:13">ngoba ngizakupha impondo zensimbi;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:13">ngizakunika amasondo ethusi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:13">njalo uzachoboza izizwe ezinengi.”</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 4:13">Uzanikela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> inzuzo yabo eyatholwa ngobuqili</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 4:13">inotho yabo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> womhlaba wonke.<verse eid="MIC 4:13"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MIC 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="MIC 5"/>
  <para style="s1">Umbusi Othenjisiweyo Ovela EBhethilehema</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MIC 5:1"/>Hlomisa amabutho akho, wena dolobho lamabutho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:1">ngoba sesivinjezelwe.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 5:1">Bazatshaya umbusi wako-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:1">esihlathini ngomqwayi.<verse eid="MIC 5:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MIC 5:2"/>“Kodwa wena Bhethilehema Efrathi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:2">lanxa umncinyane phakathi kwezizwana zakoJuda,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 5:2">kuwe kuzavela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:2">ozakuba ngumbusi wako-Israyeli,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 5:2">omdabuko wakhe ngowasekadeni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:2">kusukela ezikhathini zendulo.”<verse eid="MIC 5:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MIC 5:3"/>Ngakho u-Israyeli uzadelwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:3">kuze kube yisikhathi sokuthi lowo ohelelwayo abelethe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 5:3">laba abafowabo bonke baphenduke</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:3">ukuzahlangana labako-Israyeli.<verse eid="MIC 5:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MIC 5:4"/>Uzakuma eluse umhlambi wakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:4">ngamandla <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:4">ngobukhosi bebizo <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wakhe.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 5:4">Bazahlala ngokuvikeleka, ngoba lapho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:4">udumo lwakhe luzafika emikhawulweni yomhlaba.<verse eid="MIC 5:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MIC 5:5"/>Uzakuba yikuthula kwabo.</para>
  <para style="s1" vid="MIC 5:5">Ukukhululwa Lokuchithwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:5">Lapho umʼAsiriya ehlasela ilizwe lethu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:5">edabula phakathi kwezinqaba zethu,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 5:5">sizamvusela abelusi abayisikhombisa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:5">kanye labakhokheli babantu abayisificaminwembili.<verse eid="MIC 5:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MIC 5:6"/>Bazabusa ilizwe lase-Asiriya ngenkemba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:6">ilizwe likaNimrodi behlome ngenkemba,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 5:6">uzasikhulula kumʼAsiriya</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:6">lapho ehlasela ilizwe lethu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:6">engena phakathi kwemingcele yethu.<verse eid="MIC 5:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MIC 5:7"/>Insalela zabakoJakhobe zizakuba</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:7">phakathi kwezizwe ezinengi</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 5:7">njengamazolo avela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:7">lanjengemkhizo phezu kotshani,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 5:7">okungalindeli muntu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:7">kumbe kuhlalele abantu.<verse eid="MIC 5:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MIC 5:8"/>Insalela zabakoJakhobe zizakuba phakathi kwezizwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:8">phakathi kwabantu abanengi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 5:8">njengesilwane phakathi kwezinyamazana zegusu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:8">lanjengeguqa lesilwane phakathi komhlambi wezimvu,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 5:8">esidlithizayo sidabule ekuhambeni kwaso,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:8">kungekho ongahlenga.<verse eid="MIC 5:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MIC 5:9"/>Isandla sakho sizaphakanyiselwa phezulu ngokunqoba izitha zakho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:9">njalo zonke izitha zakho zizachithwa.<verse eid="MIC 5:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MIC 5:10"/>“Ngalolosuku,” kutsho <char style="nd">uThixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 5:10">“ngizabhubhisa amabhiza enu phakathi kwenu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:10">ngibhidlize lezinqola zenu zempi.<verse eid="MIC 5:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MIC 5:11"/>Ngizachitha amadolobho elizwe lenu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:11">ngibhidlize lezinqaba zenu zonke.<verse eid="MIC 5:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MIC 5:12"/>Ngizachitha ubuthakathi benu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:12">njalo kalisayikukhunkula futhi.<verse eid="MIC 5:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MIC 5:13"/>Ngizachitha izithombe zenu ezabazwayo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:13">lamatshe enu okukhonza phakathi kwenu;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 5:13">kalisayi kuwukhothamela futhi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:13">umsebenzi wezandla zenu.<verse eid="MIC 5:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MIC 5:14"/>Ngizasiphula phakathi kwenu izinsika zenu zika-Ashera,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:14">ngidilize lamadolobho enu.<verse eid="MIC 5:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MIC 5:15"/>Ngizaphindisela ngentukuthelo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 5:15">langolaka ezizweni ezingangilalelanga.”<verse eid="MIC 5:15"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MIC 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="MIC 6"/>
  <para style="s1">Icala Lika-Israyeli <char style="nd">KuThixo</char></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MIC 6:1"/>Lalelani okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> ukuthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 6:1">“Sukumani lilandise indaba yenu phambi kwezintaba;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:1">amaqaqa kawezwe lokho elikutshoyo.<verse eid="MIC 6:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MIC 6:2"/>Zwanini, lina zintaba, icala elethulwa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:2">lalelani lina zisekelo zomhlaba ezingulaphakade.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 6:2">Ngoba kulecala <char style="nd">uThixo</char> alibeka ebantwini bakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:2">wethesa u-Israyeli icala.<verse eid="MIC 6:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MIC 6:3"/>Bantu bami, ngenzeni kini na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:3">Ngilihluphe ngani na? Ngiphendulani.<verse eid="MIC 6:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MIC 6:4"/>Ngalikhupha eGibhithe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:4">ngalikhulula elizweni lobugqili.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 6:4">Ngathuma uMosi ukuba alikhokhele</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:4">kanye lo-Aroni loMiriyemu.<verse eid="MIC 6:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MIC 6:5"/>Bantu bami, khumbulani</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:5">izicebiso zikaBhalaki inkosi yaseMowabi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:5">lokuthi uBhalamu indodana kaBheyori waphendula wathini.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 6:5">Khumbulani uhambo lwenu kusukela eShithima kusiya eGiligali,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:5">ukuze lazi imisebenzi elungileyo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>.”<verse eid="MIC 6:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MIC 6:6"/>Kuyini engizakuza lakho phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:6">ngikhothame phambi kukaNkulunkulu ophakemeyo na?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 6:6">Ngizakuza phambi kwakhe ngilomnikelo wokutshiswa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:6">ngilamathole alomnyaka owodwa na?<verse eid="MIC 6:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MIC 6:7"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> angathokoziswa zinqama eziyizinkulungwane,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:7">izinkulungwane ezilitshumi zemifula yamafutha na?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 6:7">Ngizanikela izibulo lami ngenxa yokona kwami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:7">isithelo somzimba wami ngenxa yesono somphefumulo wami na?<verse eid="MIC 6:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MIC 6:8"/>Ukutshengisile wena muntu okuhle.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:8">
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> ufunani kuwe na?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 6:8">Ukwenza okulungileyo lokuthanda umusa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:8">kanye lokuhamba ngokuzithoba loNkulunkulu wakho.<verse eid="MIC 6:8"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Icala Lika-Israyeli Lesijeziso</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MIC 6:9"/>Lalelani! <char style="nd">UThixo</char> umemezela kulo idolobho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:9">lokwesaba ibizo lakho kuyikuhlakanipha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:9">“Qaphelani umqwayi laLowo owubekileyo.<verse eid="MIC 6:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MIC 6:10"/>Wena ndlu yobubi, kufanele lakhathesi ngiyikhohlwe inotho yakho eyazuzwa ngobubi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:10">lehefa elinganelanga, eliqalekisiweyo na?<verse eid="MIC 6:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MIC 6:11"/>Ngizamkhulula yini ecaleni umuntu olezilinganiso zobuqili,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:11">lesaka lezilinganiso zamanga na?<verse eid="MIC 6:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MIC 6:12"/>Abantu bakhona abanothileyo balochuku;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:12">abantu bakhona ngabaqambi bamanga,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:12">lezilimi zabo zikhuluma inkohliso.<verse eid="MIC 6:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MIC 6:13"/>Ngakho sengiqalisile ukukuchitha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:13">ukukuqothula ngenxa yezono zakho.<verse eid="MIC 6:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MIC 6:14"/>Uzakudla kodwa ungasuthi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:14">isisu sakho sizakuba silokhu singelalutho.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 6:14">Uzabuthelela kodwa ungalondolozi lutho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:14">ngoba lokho okulondolozayo ngizakupha inkemba.<verse eid="MIC 6:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MIC 6:15"/>Uzalima kodwa ungavuni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:15">uzakhama ama-oliva kodwa amafutha awo ungawagcobi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:15">uzakhama amavini kodwa iwayini lawo ungalinathi.<verse eid="MIC 6:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MIC 6:16"/>Ugcinile imithetho ka-Omri</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:16">layo yonke imikhutshana yasendlini ka-Ahabi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:16">walandela lamasiko abo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 6:16">Ngakho-ke ngizakunikela ekubhujisweni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:16">labantu bakho ekubeni yinhlekisa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 6:16">uzathwala ihlazo lezizwe.”<verse eid="MIC 6:16"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MIC 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="MIC 7"/>
  <para style="s1">Usizi Luka-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MIC 7:1"/>Maye ngosizi lwami!</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:1">Nginjengomuntu obutha izithelo zehlobo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:1">senginjengevini eselivunwe laphela;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:1">akuselasixha samavini okudliwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:1">kayisekho lemikhiwa yakuqala engiyikhanukayo.<verse eid="MIC 7:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MIC 7:2"/>Abathembekileyo babhujisiwe elizweni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:2">kakho lamunye umuntu olungileyo oseleyo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:2">Abantu bonke bacathamela ukuchitha igazi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:2">lowo lalowo uzingela umfowabo ngombule.<verse eid="MIC 7:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MIC 7:3"/>Izandla zombili zizingcitshi ekwenzeni okubi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:3">umbusi ufuna izipho ngamandla,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:3">umahluleli wamukela isivalamlomo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:3">abalamandla babiza abakufisayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:3">bonke baceba okubi bendawonye.<verse eid="MIC 7:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MIC 7:4"/>Ongcono wabo unjengesihlahla sameva,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:4">oqotho kakhulu mubi kulothango lwameva.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:4">Usuku uNkulunkulu alethekelela ngalo selufikile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:4">usuku lokukhala kophondo lwabalindi.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:4">Manje sekuyisikhathi sokuphumputheka kwabo.<verse eid="MIC 7:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MIC 7:5"/>Ungamethembi umakhelwane;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:5">ungagwabi ngomngane wakho.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:5">Lalowo olala umgonile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:5">qaphela amazwi akho.<verse eid="MIC 7:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MIC 7:6"/>Ngoba indodana idumaza uyise,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:6">indodakazi ivukela unina,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:6">umalukazana avukele uninazala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:6">izitha zomuntu ngamalunga endlu yakhe.<verse eid="MIC 7:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MIC 7:7"/>Kodwa mina ngilindele <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ngethemba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:7">ngilindele uNkulunkulu uMsindisi wami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:7">uNkulunkulu wami uzangizwa.<verse eid="MIC 7:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">U-Israyeli Uzavuka</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MIC 7:8"/>Ungaklolodi wena sitha sami!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:8">Lanxa ngiwile, ngizavuka.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:8">Lanxa ngihlezi emnyameni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:8">
    <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uzakuba yikukhanya kwami.<verse eid="MIC 7:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MIC 7:9"/>Ngenxa yokuba ngonile kuye,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:9">ngizalumela ulaka <char style="nd">lukaThixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:9">aze angincengele endabeni yami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:9">aveze ukungabi lacala kwami.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:9">Uzangikhuphela phandle ekukhanyeni;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:9">ngizabona ukulunga kwakhe.<verse eid="MIC 7:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MIC 7:10"/>Lapho-ke isitha sami sizakubona,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:10">njalo sibanjwe zinhloni,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:10">lowo owathi kimi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:10">“Ungaphi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wakho?”</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:10">Lakhathesi uzagxotshwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:10">ngezinyawo njengodaka emigwaqweni.<verse eid="MIC 7:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MIC 7:11"/>Usuku lokwakhiwa kwemiduli yakho luzafika,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:11">usuku lokuqhelisa imingcele yakho.<verse eid="MIC 7:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MIC 7:12"/>Ngalolosuku abantu bazakuza kuwe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:12">bevela e-Asiriya lasemadolobheni aseGibhithe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:12">njalo kusukela eGibhithe kusiya kuYufrathe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:12">kusukela olwandle kusiya olwandle,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:12">lakusukela entabeni kusiya entabeni.<verse eid="MIC 7:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MIC 7:13"/>Umhlaba uzachitheka ngenxa yabahlezi kuwo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:13">ngenxa yezenzo zabo.<verse eid="MIC 7:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukukhuleka Lokudumisa</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MIC 7:14"/>Beluse abantu bakho ngentonga yakho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:14">umhlambi welifa lakho,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:14">ohlala wodwa ehlathini</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:14">emadlelweni avundileyo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:14">Kawudle eBhashani laseGiliyadi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:14">njengasezinsukwini zokuphuma.<verse eid="MIC 7:14"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MIC 7:15"/>“Njengasezinsukwini zokuphuma kwenu eGibhithe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:15">ngizabatshengisa izimangaliso zami.”<verse eid="MIC 7:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MIC 7:16"/>Izizwe zizabona ziyangeke,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:16">zemukwe wonke amandla azo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:16">Zizabamba imilomo yazo ngezandla,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:16">lezindlebe zazo zingabe zisezwa.<verse eid="MIC 7:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MIC 7:17"/>Zizakhotha uthuli njengenyoka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:17">njengezinanakazana ezihuquzela emhlabathini.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:17">Zizakuza ziqhaqhazela ziphuma emihomeni yazo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:17">zizaphendukela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu ngokwesaba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:17">njalo lawe zizakwesaba.<verse eid="MIC 7:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MIC 7:18"/>Ngubani onguNkulunkulu njengawe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:18">oxolela izono athethelele iziphambeko</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:18">zensalela zelifa lakhe na?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:18">Kawuthukutheli kokuphela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:18">kodwa uthokoza ngokutshengisa isihawu.<verse eid="MIC 7:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MIC 7:19"/>Uzakuba lesihawu kithi futhi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:19">uzanyathela izono zethu ngezinyawo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:19">uphosele bonke ububi bethu ezinzikini zolwandle.<verse eid="MIC 7:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MIC 7:20"/>Uzakuba qotho kuJakhobe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:20">ubonakalise isihawu sakho ku-Abhrahama,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MIC 7:20">njengokuthembisa kwakho ngesifungo kubokhokho bethu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MIC 7:20">ensukwini zasendulo.<verse eid="MIC 7:20"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MIC 7"/>
</usx>
